name: Create a Offer for Car insurance (Old timer) -- @1.1 Test data for Offer -> Car insurance (Old timer)

steps.name: * Set resource name for locators Argenta
* Log in to the application
* Choose Car for offer "insurance" drop-down menu
* Select a distributor with id 3588
* Click Search Person link
* Fill Lamxxxxxxx in search owner page "First name" field
* Click Search Owner page Search button
* Click Referential first search result
* Click Risk button
* Click Add Old timer button
* Fill Rolls Royce in Add Old timer => Vehicle details page => Make  field
* Fill Phantom in Add Old timer => Vehicle details page => Model field
* Fill 5 in Add Old timer => Vehicle details page => Version field
* Choose Old timer private car for Add Old timer => Vehicle details page => Vehicle type drop-down menu
* Fill 100 in Offer => Add Old timer => Vehicle details page => Power field
* Fill 09/09/1990 in Add Old timer => Vehicle details page => First use date field
* Fill 5 in Add Old timer => Vehicle details page => Number of seats field
* Fill O1111CA in Add Old timer => Vehicle details page => Registration number field
* Fill 11183765 in Add Old timer => Vehicle details page => Chassis number field
* Choose Normal Plate for Add Car => Vehicle details page => Registration type options area
* Choose Electric for Add Car => Vehicle details page => Fuel type options area
* Choose Private for Add Car => vehicle details page => Usage type options area
* Click Next button
* Click Add Car => Claim history page => Add claim button
* Choose Accident for Add car => Add claim => Nature drop-down menu
* Fill 08/08/2018 in Add car => Add claim => Date field
* Choose 0 percent for Add car => Add claim => Liability drop-down menu
* Choose Primary for Add car => Add claim => Driver type drop-down menu
* Fill 08/08/1980 in Add car => Add claim => Driver date of birth field
* Choose Yes for Add car => Add claim => Joker used options area
* Fill 3000 in Add car => Add claim => Amount field
* Choose No for Add car => Add claim => Risk fully repaired options area
* Click Add car => Add claim => OK button
* Click Add Old timer => Claim history page => Next button
* Click Offer => Add old timer => Drivers page => Add driver button
* Click Add Old timer => Add driver => Next button
* Fill 74898744 in Offer => Add car => Driver license page => "License ID" field
* Fill 12/02/2019 in Offer => Add car => Add driver => Driver license page => license date field
* Choose B for Offer => Add car => Add driver => Driver license page => license category options area
* Click Offer => Add Old timer => Add driver => Driver license page => Next button
* Click Offer => Add Old timer => Add driver => Address page => Next button
* Click Offer => Add Old timer => Add driver => Contact page => Next button
* Click Offer => Add Old timer => Add driver page => OK button
* Click Offer => Add Old timer => Drivers page => Next button
* Click Offer => Add Old timer page => Previous insurer => "Next" button
* Choose No for Offer => Add Old timer => Risk background page => Certificates options area
* Click Offer => Add Old timer => Risk background page => Certificates => Next button
* Click OK button
* Click  "Coverage tariffs" button
* Choose Legal assistance safe for Offer => Add Old timer => Coverage tariffs page options area
* Click Billing button
* Choose Direct credit for Billing page => Type options area
* Choose Annual for Billing page => Frequency options area
* Fill 13 in Billing renewal day field
* Fill 5 in Billing renewal month field
* Click Risk acceptance button
* Click Risk acceptance answer button
* Click Summary button
* Click Submission button
* Wait for Offer congratulations message
* Verify Offer congratulations message contains Your proposition with number text

fullName: Create Offer: Create a Offer for Car insurance (Old timer)
